1258c035929ed3","tid":1670491,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31fc0e7d6cf2ed4436b37205fd8e8433ed8931e7","tid":1670491,"uid":12444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"gphone 真係進化得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:50:26.000Z","msg":"仲有戴耀庭都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99a42735ea4a0f8f16068622dd29eec4c911f05","tid":1670491,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">疑似三毛不斷無限放大「加泰左膠舉共產黨旗」去抹黑加泰人支持共產主義</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n黃之峰都忍唔住出聲支持加泰集會 (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670496/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670496/page/1</a>)，建議BLOCK晒所有以偏概全散播假消息抹黑既ACCOUNT：<br />\n<br />\n會員：Miami #110123<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670385/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670385/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n會員：我一直關注事件 #176282<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670272/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670272/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員：無知無我 #208086<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670421/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670421/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員：Toni_kroos8 #36775<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1670572/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1670572/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係加泰左膠：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/vGKcF3t.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係香港都有「社會主義行動」咁解囉, 只係極少數ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將一少撮非主流既人去無限放大, 帶風向, 係乜嘢居心? 係咪HK01？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170109/s00046/f8dcd60bf999b734832ad2a8a3946fc5.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i1.wp.com/polymerhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1619385_446866478773887_1096852778_n.jpg?w=720\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加泰人支持共產主義？<br />\n<br />\n加泰羅尼亞係西班牙最富有既地區，係西班牙既香港嚟架！"},{"pid":"c1a69816664ba1f10f8e8e4d6e790884cb18c336","tid":1670491,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}